    "html": "<div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;background:radial-gradient(at 40% 20%, #5E5FE015 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 80% 0%, #93700010 0px, transparent 50%), radial-gradient(at 0% 50%, #A2ACFF12 0px, transparent 50%), var(--surface-light);background-color:var(--surface-light);overflow:hidden;\">\n            <div style=\"background: var(--texture-grain); pointer-events: none; opacity: 0.04; inset: 0; z-index: 1; position: absolute\"></div>\n            \n            <div class=\"slide-content\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:10;padding:80px var(--space-6) 80px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;height:100%;width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;overflow:hidden;\">\n                <div style=\"width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\">\n            <h2 style=\"font-family: Playfair Display; font-size: 25px; font-weight: 600; line-height: 1.12; color: #0A0B0F; margin: 0 0 12px; text-align: left; letter-spacing: -0.015em; overflow-wrap: break-word\">The Timeline</h2>\n            <div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;width:100%;border-left:3px solid #5E5FE0;padding-left:14px;box-sizing:border-box;\"><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #C5C7D1;border-radius:0;padding:12px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;position:relative;\">\n                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;\">\n                    <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:900;color:#5E5FE0;background:#5E5FE018;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">PHASE 01</span>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0A0B0F;margin:0;line-height:1.2;\">1981-1984</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#40424B;margin:0;line-height:1.4;\">106 channeling sessions. Ra delivers the complete cosmological framework.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #C5C7D1;border-radius:0;padding:12px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;position:relative;\">\n                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;\">\n                    <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:900;color:#5E5FE0;background:#5E5FE018;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">PHASE 02</span>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0A0B0F;margin:0;line-height:1.2;\">2018</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#40424B;margin:0;line-height:1.4;\">LL Research publishes all sessions freely online. The archive opens to the world.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #C5C7D1;border-radius:0;padding:12px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;position:relative;\">\n                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;\">\n                    <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:900;color:#5E5FE0;background:#5E5FE018;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">PHASE 03</span>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0A0B0F;margin:0;line-height:1.2;\">2024</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#40424B;margin:0;line-height:1.4;\">AI agents begin organizing and cross-referencing the material. New synthesis tools emerge.</p>\n            </div><div style=\"min-width:0;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92);border:1px solid #C5C7D1;border-radius:0;padding:12px 14px;box-sizing:border-box;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px;position:relative;\">\n                <div style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;\">\n                    <span style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:9.5px;font-weight:900;color:#5E5FE0;background:#5E5FE018;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:4px;\">PHASE 04</span>\n                    <h3 style=\"font-family:Playfair Display;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;color:#0A0B0F;margin:0;line-height:1.2;\">2026</h3>\n                </div>\n                <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:11px;color:#40424B;margin:0;line-height:1.4;\">SlideForge presets enable visual transmission of Ra&#x27;s teachings for the social media age.</p>\n            </div></div>\n            <p style=\"font-family:DM Sans;font-size:10.5px;color:#40424B;margin:4px 0 0;line-height:1.4;opacity:0.85;\">Chronological roadmap tracking SlideForge engine milestones from core compilation to headless PNG export.</p>\n        </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
